text.section:
The Commission shall advance cooperation between the Commonwealth and other units of government by exercising principal responsibility and authority for:
The proposing of compacts;
The proposing of uniform laws, model laws, and reciprocal statutes;
The encouraging of uniform or reciprocal administrative rules and regulations;
The interchange and clearance of research and information; and
Any other intergovernmental action, agreement, or process that affects intergovernmental cooperation.
